 \sum \limits_{k=1}^{n} \frac{k}{n^k}{n\choose k}
n-k = (n-1) - (k-1)
   \sum_{k=1}^n \frac{k}{n^k}\binom{n}{k} = \sum_{k=1}^n \frac{1}{n^{k-1}}\frac{(n-1)!}{(k-1)!(n-k)!} = \sum_{k=1}^n \left(\frac{1}{n}\right)^{k-1} \binom{n-1}{k-1} 
   \sum_{k=1}^n \frac{k}{n^k}\binom{n}{k} = \sum_{k=0}^{n-1} \left(\frac{1}{n}\right)^k \binom{n-1}{k} = \left(1 + \frac{1}{n}\right)^{n-1} 
